Based on https://github.com/waveshareteam/ESP32-S3-PhotoPainter/tree/56c5498c44490cec4feef35d5f00cdac6b6dba26/01_Example/xiaozhi-esp32
Only differences are tracked in this directory.

The modified version will:
- Fetch and show an image from iot.home/7.sp6 on boot, and on pressing "boot".
- Reuses xiaozhi's wifi connection setup logic.
- Deep sleep for 1 day.
